        <Parent_String>people in literature-related occupations [300171575], people in literature and related occupations [300171573], people in the humanities [300025485], people by occupation [300024980], people (agents) [300024979], People (hierarchy name) [300024978], Agents Facet [300264089]</Parent_String>
